body_text:
@apaszke
The problem here is not disk-io (since disk-io not blocking GIL), but serialization/deserialization. And you can't use process, because you need serialize object to pass it to another process, then process will deserialize it and serialize again to write to disk 😄
Since this is pickle «problem», I think issue can be closed.

